sentences.english: And let there be no mistake: The blood is definitely running right now on Wall Street.
sentences.chinese: 毋庸贅言，現在華爾街的確已經是血流成河了。

sentences.english: We need some fresh blood- that's for sure.

sentences.english: No one should doubt our commitment to Afghanistan and its people.
sentences.chinese: 我們對阿富汗及其人民的承諾是毋庸置疑的。

sentences.english: His brilliance renders this film an indubitable classic.

sentences.english: There is no doubt that they will be the champion of the CSL, (short for China's Super League).

sentences.english: But we have to admit that the system still has a few aspects needed to be consummated immediately.

sentences.english: It would not be easy, no question about that. But we have counting rules now.

sentences.english: It goes without saying that the Chinese ink painting holds very particular connotations.
sentences.chinese: 毋庸置疑，水墨作爲畫材具有非常特殊的意義。

sentences.english: The facticity of manuscript is indubitability.
sentences.chinese: 手稿的真實性是毋庸置疑。

sentences.english: Sure, we all know that Valentine's Day is a racket.

sentences.english: You have had by any standards a spectacular career.
sentences.chinese: 毋庸置疑，您的教學生涯非常璀璨。

sentences.english: Needless to say, all the above are more useful than revenge and disrespect.

sentences.english: When it comes to Western tech companies, Google is unmistakably ahead of the curve.
sentences.chinese: 提到西方科技公司，谷歌毋庸置疑高瞻遠矚。

sentences.english: Technology has imposed the encumbrance of over-choice on us.
sentences.chinese: 毋庸置疑，技術造成了多重選擇的困境。

sentences.english: I have no doubt it will be a noteworthy experience.
sentences.chinese: 毋庸置疑這將是一次非常值得嘗試的經歷。
